That's the lceman!

674
01:25:27,110 --> 01:25:31,690
Pretty good, Jack.
You always were a smart cop.

675
01:25:31,860 --> 01:25:36,990
- l really didn't want to believe it.
- Sorry to let you down, Jack.

676
01:25:37,490 --> 01:25:41,290
