You two, take the money and leave.

677
01:25:41,450 --> 01:25:45,420
- Nobody is leaving with my money.
- Money?. l want the fucking lceman.

678
01:26:04,980 --> 01:26:07,440
Get the fuck out of the way.

679
01:27:04,910 --> 01:27:06,910
Fuck!

680
01:27:26,100 --> 01:27:31,190
- Somebody help me!
- Shut up!

681
01:27:31,360 --> 01:27:33,270
Let go of me.

682
01:27:35,110 --> 01:27:39,860
You fucking bitch!

683
01:28:09,980 --> 01:28:16,400
You set me up, Ben.
You never ran that shit through NClC.

684
01:28:16,570 --> 01:28:19,700
